  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/ae78bc105c2c1c5842955366aec65df7.poster.avif?t=1726617114\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/ae78bc105c2c1c5842955366aec65df7.webm?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/ae78bc105c2c1c5842955366aec65df7.mp4?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/665961618a5a176322cffa2c23e7ae0b.avif?t=1726617114\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Collect resources</strong> to expand your village, build houses, raise villagers and improve your defense.</li></ul>In ignis corruption, resources act as the base currency for the creation of your world, choose well where you will allocate them or suffer the consequences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/097a19e2bca33a20da81093b2e33bd22.poster.avif?t=1726617114\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/097a19e2bca33a20da81093b2e33bd22.webm?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/097a19e2bca33a20da81093b2e33bd22.mp4?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/26a99116b48aca36ef33b38f25d7d61d.avif?t=1726617114\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The <strong>strategic positioning</strong> of your buildings is essential to follow a successful path.</li></ul><br>Place extractors for wood, stone, iron and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/3106f85d7f106fd6f75004804c8e94a4.poster.avif?t=1726617114\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/3106f85d7f106fd6f75004804c8e94a4.webm?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/3106f85d7f106fd6f75004804c8e94a4.mp4?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/8ef9bc731018425d8c6e723444b411eb.avif?t=1726617114\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fighting to survive</strong> is a small part of a much larger task.</li></ul><br>Fight enemies, survive natural disasters, supply your village, send resources, grow your community, locate and destroy the source of evil.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/15bb5a98869f6e2c77426d1398d148a2.poster.avif?t=1726617114\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/15bb5a98869f6e2c77426d1398d148a2.webm?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825130/extras/15bb5a98869f6e2c77426d1398d148a2.mp4?t=1726617114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stylized Graphics<br></li><li>City building system<br></li><li>Unit control system<br></li><li>Resource collection system<br></li><li>Food planting system<br></li><li>Natural disaster system<br></li><li>Classic RTS style camera controls<br></li><li>Library for researching new technologies<br></li><li>Market to trade resources<br></li><li>Quest system<br></li><li>Procedural Map</li></ul>",
